fields.name: Padel Field - Jakarta
fields.description: A premium padel field in South Jakarta, equipped with night lighting and modern facilities. High demand for bookings from sports communities and corporate events.

fields.name: Futsal Arena - Bandung
fields.description: A popular futsal arena in Bandung with 3 indoor courts, locker rooms, and a cafe. Regularly hosts local tournaments and leagues.

fields.name: Swimming Pool Complex - Surabaya
fields.description: An Olympic-size swimming pool complex in Surabaya, open to the public and used for regional competitions. Includes a gym and cafe.

fields.name: Badminton Hall - Medan
fields.description: A modern badminton hall in Medan with 8 courts, pro shop, and training academy. Hosts national and local tournaments.

fields.name: Fitness Center - Bali
fields.description: A luxury fitness center in Bali with state-of-the-art equipment, group classes, and spa facilities. Popular with locals and tourists.

fields.name: Climbing Gym - Yogyakarta
fields.description: A new indoor climbing gym in Yogyakarta, offering bouldering, top-rope, and lead climbing. Hosts regular competitions and training camps.
